Reasoning: The paper deals with the performance evaluation of a wireless link under different fading conditions, which is a common topic in the field of Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networked Systems (cs.NI). The use of MIMO and SIMO/MISO models also suggests a focus on signal processing and communication systems (cs.SY). The incorporation of Transmitting Antenna Selection (TAS) and modulation schemes further supports the relevance to Multimedia (cs.MM) and Computer Communications (cs.COM).
